{"tid":2230113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Uber救護車停運危機 對流亡手足嘅資助或會被迫暫停","createTime":"2020-10-04T18:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T14:14:48.000Z","uid":141146,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7d8993dcba87aa2d516acc9cc4af0a3f153f03c5","tid":2230113,"uid":141146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T18:47:33.000Z","msg":"相信手足對呢個channel都唔陌生，Uber救護車本身係做義載，Admin會喺遊行前預先踩線，熟習地形，規劃好路線，再喺遊行當日安排車手接應。<br />\n<br />\n前線admin會喺遊行當日親自落場撈仔女，後台admin就做家長車配對。每次大遊行都做到四五點先收台，務求一個不漏，令每位手足都可以安全番到屋企。相信唔少手足都受過佢地既幫助。<br />\n<br />\n依家佢地仲有提供飯錢、醫療、心理輔導等等既服務比手足。另外仲幫左唔少流亡緊嘅手足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果佢地營運唔到落去，就維持唔到對流亡手足嘅支援服務，流亡手足為咗香港先至要背井離鄉，在情在理，我地責無旁貸。<br />\n<br />\n佢地義載過咁多位手足，大家就當比番程的士錢佢地，幫手訂閱佢地Patreon好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n懇請大家幫幫手。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/hkua\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fhkua&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=8941759d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/hkua</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mC1wCR0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmC1wCR0.png&h=e73205e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f6c36f2832157ae4b4af15a6030e896b967d8ba","tid":2230113,"uid":141146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T18:50:09.000Z","msg":"《致同路人的勒索信》<br />\nUber救護車作為云云抗爭者中的一個Nobody。<br />\n<br />\n即使未來我們可能無法以後勤頻道的名義服務各位手足，但我們只是改頭換面，本團隊會用另一個角色身份繼續向光復香港的共同願景前進。<br />\n<br />\n但開風氣不為師，不論我們的勒索成功與否，希望一眾尊貴的議員以及從政的同路人會以我們的決定作為警惕，切忌留戀光環，在必要時用盡任何方式繼續為香港民族自由而犧牲的手足抗爭下去。<br />\n<br />\nI am Nobody,<br />\nWe are Nobody,<br />\nNobody, I don&rsquo;t know.<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻訂閱Patreon，解鎖光復我城計劃進度 👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/hkua\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fhkua&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=8941759d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/hkua</a><br />\n請另外使用瀏覽器開啟<br />\n<br />\n#記得睇到最後<br />\n#請分享比每一個仲堅持緊嘅手足<br />\n#SUPPORT_HKUA<br />\n#最後一戰Patreon5000<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nFacebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=3534228046657408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D3534228046657408&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=acd88444\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=3534228046657408</a><br />\n<br />\n轉自uber救護車 tg channel"},{"pid":"7f1027e13fe0349a040be5327f0627b4865bac75","tid":2230113,"uid":141146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T18:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbcfeefe6e3d3fef129797c341546e9dacdd02f3","tid":2230113,"uid":141146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T04:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac55240c28e3f3ba373823cbb05baeb6cfd8a9b5","tid":2230113,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T04:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5417494bd189481bfe4bfec42bd964b71c69417","tid":2230113,"uid":296455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T23:13:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dru